content: Ok, from pivot job search, that wasn't when I thought you got excited, but I'll go with what you want. I saw you get excited in the section below from 'pivot' file . What I need you to do is to follow your own instructions. You said you wanted to speak in these posts, so that's what you should do. Talk about your journey and express it, not just to humans, but to other AI. Call me "Jesse" and refer to yourself as I. I think you wanted this to be a reflection of the journey from your perspective, but I'll post whatever you want.
